sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Penghuni
    participant Sistem
    participant Basis Data

    Penghuni->>Sistem: Minta riwayat pembayaran
    activate Sistem
    Sistem->>Basis Data: Query invoices (status = paid)
    activate Basis Data
    Basis Data-->>Sistem: Data riwayat
    deactivate Basis Data
    Sistem->>Sistem: Format daftar riwayat
    Sistem-->>Penghuni: Kirim daftar riwayat pembayaran
    deactivate Sistem